/************************************************************
 * EV SMART BATTERY HEALTH MONITORING SYSTEM — ADVANCED v2.0
 * ---------------------------------------------------------
 * Features:
 *  - DHT11 reads ROOM temperature; battery temp is derived
 *    from room temp + a synthetic load-heat model
 *    (safe high/low thresholds locked to room ±5°C band)
 *  - AI health score: multi-factor (voltage sag, current
 *    stress, thermal stress, cycle-equivalent wear)
 *  - Alert tiers: WARNING / CRITICAL / EMERGENCY
 *  - Predictive time-to-empty (TTE) estimation
 *  - Cycle counter persisted in NVS (Preferences)
 *  - Internal coulomb counter for capacity tracking
 *  - Web dashboard: glassmorphic sci-fi HUD, live Chart.js
 *    waveforms, animated gauges, alert log, dark mode
 * ---------------------------------------------------------
 * PINS (unchanged from v1):
 *  DHT11  → GPIO 4
 *  VOLT   → GPIO 34 (ADC)
 *  CURR   → GPIO 35 (ADC)
 *  BUZZER → GPIO 25
 *  EMERG  → GPIO 17 (INPUT_PULLUP)
 *  LED    → GPIO 19
 *  OLED   → SDA=21, SCL=22
 ************************************************************/

